rComments: Best crim prof out there! I found theories boring before but I loved these. Uses lots of examples & videos in his detailed explanations to make sure you understand. Clear grading criteria- 2 midterms. Very passionate about what hes teaching even through recorded lectures. Take his class you wont regret it. He also has a very soothing voice
Such a good Prof, really explains what he wants in his exams and midterms. Clear and concise. Would definitely take his class again!

Always show up to class and make sure to write everything he says down. Study tip : Reread what he said in class multiple times and make sure to UNDERSTAND. Understanding is what will make you pass. If you have questions, make an appointment with him. Don't zone out because you'll have trouble following after. I love him overall.

I have had many peers say he is a great prof. He is good, however I am did not find his class very interesting. He is VERY wordy and takes a long time to explain few concepts. It did make the exams less work in the end, but I had to buy coffees for his classes just to stay awake.
Mon meilleur professeur à date ! Il est passionnant et passionné !

the best teacher i've had

By far the best Prof I've ever had! He structures his lectures in a way that makes it very easy to understand the concepts and he explains them extremely well. Richard Dubé est le meilleur professeur en criminologie . Il connais la matière qu'il enseigne et sa méthode d'enseigner est excellente.
